      Requirements:
        Apache 2.x with PHP 5.1 or later
        either MySQL 5.0 or later or SQLite 3.x or later or PostgreSQL 
        a web-browser (doh!)

      Summary:
        Prails let's you easily create complex PHP applications in almost no time.
        For a summary of features, please see the documentation.

      Download:
        You can get the newest version at http://prails.org/.

      Installation:
        Please see the documentation.

      Documentation:
        Basic documentation available at http://prails.org/static/documentation.html.


    Enjoy!
       Your Prails-"Team"
        
